('33cb64a0-cd33-11e8-9725-8b6f81505fb4', 'Design and Development of Universal Engine Oil filter Wrench', '\"[{\\\"id\\\":0,\\\"name\\\":\\\"PROF. VIRGILIO T. OMBAO\\\"}]\"', '<h3>Abstract</h3><br><table class=\"MsoTableGrid\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"938\" style=\"width: 703.2pt; border: none;\">\r\n <tbody><tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:0;mso-yfti-firstrow:yes;mso-yfti-lastrow:yes;\r\n  height:73.15pt\">\r\n  <td width=\"117\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:87.95pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt;height:73.15pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n  normal\"><span lang=\"EN-PH\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt\">Technology\r\n  has changed many things and made life comfortable. The study aimed to design\r\n  and develop a more convenient universal engine oil filter wrench that is\r\n  beneficial to the technician and would make his/her task easy. The study used\r\n  the developmental research design and descriptive measures such as frequency\r\n  counting, percentages, and weighted mean. The instruments used in the study\r\n  includes questionnaire for the profile of the respondents and to test the\r\n  functionality of the universal oil filter wrench itself. A quantitative\r\n  interpretation was used to construe the data. The study revealed that the\r\n  designed and developed oil filter wrench is highly functional; majority of\r\n  the respondents rated the tool as highly functional with a mean of 4.73. It\r\n  is functioning well; it is tested for numerous times and after the revisions\r\n  to the study, the researcher recommended that the diameter of the aluminum\r\n  tube and the size of the three holders be reduced and the three holders should\r\n  be made removable. For servicing, a mass production of the tool and\r\n  dissemination of the project to automotive shops is also recommend.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n </tr>\r\n</tbody></table>', 'Assessment,percent cover,mangroves,seagrass,corals,water quality', 1, 7, 63, '2018-01-01', '2018-12-01', 'Usep- Research division/ University Funded Project', '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Usep-Bislig R#5.pdf', 182753, 1, 1, '5ed3c6a0-c880-11e8-9bd6-e11af0701d8a', '2018-10-11 00:54:03', '2018-10-11 00:54:03'),
