he flowering pattern this due climate change and the impact of seed\r\n  collection technology applied in previous (2008) seed collection.<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n </tr>\r\n</tbody></table>', 'Flowering and Fruiting,f Paserianthes falcate (Mollucan sau)', 2, 10, 92, '2008-01-01', '2009-12-01', 'Usep- Research division/ University Funded Project', '42000.00', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Flowering and Fruiting Habits of Paserian falcate.pdf', 418363, 1, 1, '5ed3c6a0-c880-11e8-9bd6-e11af0701d8a', '2018-10-18 22:08:53', '2018-10-18 22:08:53'),
