('cd158880-d75a-11e8-9783-673796301236', 'Trends and Projections of the Licensure Examination Performances of Education Graduates of Agusan del Sur State College of Agriculture and Technology', '\"[{\\\"id\\\":0,\\\"name\\\":\\\"Carlito P. Yurangco Ph.D.\\\"}]\"', '<h3>Abstract</h3><br><table class=\"MsoTableGrid\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"1002\" style=\"margin-left: -0.25pt; border: none;\">\r\n <tbody><tr>\r\n  <td width=\"162\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:121.5pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">This study aimed to\r\n  determine the trends and projections of the Licensure Examination\r\n  Performances of College of Teacher Education graduates of Agusan Del Sur\r\n  State College of Agriculture and Technology from 2018 to 2015. The study used\r\n  authentic secondary data obtained from Professional Regulation Commission\r\n  (PRC), Butuan City, in Caraga Region. To analyze the data, Time Series Trend\r\n  analysis was applied. It was found out that the trend model of the LET\r\n  performance of BEED was y = 11.923 + 2.43t and for PRC was y = 22.03 +\r\n  1.38t.&nbsp; Using both models to project\r\n  the Licensure performance for 5 years, the study revealed that by 2020, BEED\r\n  will just be 3.61% above the national passing rate which is way below the 25%\r\n  above the national passing rate required by AACCUP. On the other hand, the\r\n  model for the performance of BSEd was y = 7.94 + 2.82t and for the PRC was y\r\n  = 25.17 + 1.38t. Using both models, in 2020, the Licensure examination\r\n  performance of Bachelor of Secondary Education passing rate will just be\r\n  1.48% above the national passing rate which is way below the 25% above the\r\n  national passing rate required by AACCUP.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n  normal\"><o:p style=\"\">&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n </tr>\r\n</tbody></table>', 'Trends and Projections,Licensure Examination for Teachers (LET) ,Licensure Performance', 4, 23, 228, '2018-01-01', '2018-12-01', 'Agusan del Sur State College of Agriculture and Technology', '17000.00', 'Agusan del Sur', NULL, NULL, 'Agusan del Sur State College of Agriculture and Technology  Research.pdf', 328989, 1, 0, '5ed3c6a0-c880-11e8-9bd6-e11af0701d8a', '2018-10-23 23:02:42', '2018-10-23 23:02:42'),
